sky.engine.util
Class VisitorMap<K,L>

java.lang.Object
  sky.engine.util.VisitorMap<K,L>
Type Parameters:
K - - Class type for the Keys.
L - - Class type for the Links of the Keys.
public class VisitorMap<K,L>
extends java.lang.Object

A data structure for storing a set of Keys, each with a set of Links; keeping in memory whether those Links have been visited to from their parent Key.

Since:
24 May 2012. (Last update: 24 May 2012).
Version:
1.0.0.
Author:
Matthew Kelly (Badgerati).
